room_title: Escape room "Under Pressure" by Escapology Rockwall in Dallas-Fort Worth
review: This was an awesome room! My wife and I did under pressure, their hardest one! We were able to escape but props to our Game Master Ian, he was helpful with clues and was great help!! We have done like 10 different escape room but definitely would rate them top 3!
